Media aide to former Governor Ayodele Peter Fayose of Ekiti State, Lere Olayinka has reacted to the photos of the deplorable conditions of some roads in Lagos State, Southwest geopolitical zone of the country.

Lagos State is the main commercial hub of the country with people from different parts of the country living in it.

Reacting to the photos of the horrible roads, Lere Olayinka who is known for his outspokenness said this is ‘their Lagos’.
The Peoples Democratic Party chieftain and veteran Journalist claimed that the road is at Ijanikin in Lagos State.

The recent post by Lere Olayinka on his verified Facebook page has generated a lot of reactions from his fans and numerous followers on the social media platform.


